      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not required at MRL 2; qualitative mapping between experimental and simulation inputs documented.",
      "rationale": "Qualitative mapping table confirms that simulation boundary conditions correspond to reported experimental settings. Formal equivalency quantification not required at MRL 2."
    }
