    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. The 6 not-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out per ASME V&V 40 MRL 2 requirements. CFD hemolysis predictions demonstrate sufficient credibility for identifying worst-case operating conditions in the Class II CPB device design space. The assessment team concludes the model is fit for the intended pre-market design-space exploration purpose as described in the claim and requirement documentation.",
